OL,3,CLabour Government accused of
OL,4,C'betraying' Troubles victims
OL,6,FThe Labour Government has been accused
OL,7,Fof "betraying" victims of Northern
OL,8,FIreland's Troubles.
OL,10,FMartina Dillon, whose husband Seamus
OL,11,Fwas shot dead in a loyalist attack at
OL,12,Fthe Glengannon Hotel in Dungannon, Co
OL,13,FTyrone, in 1997, said she has been
OL,14,Ffighting for decades to learn the
OL,15,Ftruth of what happened.
OL,17,FShe was reacting after a decision by
OL,18,Fthe Government to challenge a critical
OL,19,Fjudgment by the Court of Appeal in
OL,20,FBelfast on the previous government's
OL,21,FLegacy Act.
OL,26,@oD@DOUoD@NO]
