OL,3,CLabour Government accused of
OL,4,C'betraying' Troubles victims
OL,6,FThe Act halted legacy inquests, and
OL,7,Fset up the Independent Commission for
OL,8,FReconciliation and Information
OL,9,FRecovery (ICRIR) to look into cases
OL,10,Ffrom the past. Scores of bereaved
OL,11,Ffamilies have opposed this, and are
OL,12,Fcalling for inquests to be restored.
OL,14,FLast month, three Court of Appeal
OL,15,Fjudges ruled that a Government veto
OL,16,Fpower over what sensitive material can
OL,17,Fbe disclosed to bereaved families by
OL,18,Fthe Act's ICRIR is incompatible with
OL,19,Fhuman rights laws.
