OL,3,CLabour Government accused of
OL,4,C'betraying' Troubles victims
OL,6,FThey also found that the work of the
OL,7,Fcommission also does not provide
OL,8,Fvictims and their next of kin adequate
OL,9,Fmeans to participate in its processes.
OL,11,FHowever, other grounds of the appeal
OL,12,Ftaken by the victims were dismissed,
OL,13,Fincluding the challenge over its
OL,14,Foperational independence.
OL,16,FOn Friday it emerged that the
OL,17,FGovernment are seeking to challenge
OL,18,Fthat judgment.
