OL,3,CLabour Government accused of
OL,4,C'betraying' Troubles victims
OL,6,FMeanwhile the Irish Government were
OL,7,Furged to "hold to" its interstate case
OL,8,Fagainst the UK over the Legacy Act.
OL,10,FOn Monday, Troubles victims, supported
OL,11,Fby Amnesty International UK and
OL,12,FPhoenix Law expressed their concern at
OL,13,Fthe move to appeal, pointing to
OL,14,Findications by Labour before the
OL,15,Felection that it would repeal and
OL,16,Freplace the Act.
OL,18,FMs Dillon said it is "absolutely
OL,19,Fdisgusting the way that we have been
OL,20,Ftreated".
