OL,3,CLabour Government accused of
OL,4,C'betraying' Troubles victims
OL,6,FShe described news of the Government's
OL,7,Fintention to appeal as "a complete
OL,8,Fshock".
OL,10,F"I put my faith in the Government. The
OL,11,Fday Labour got in I was so happy, and
OL,12,Fthen to hear on Friday evening that
OL,13,Fthey are taking a legal challenge
OL,14,Fagainst our court winnings, absolutely
OL,15,Fdisgusted with Labour," she said.
