OL,3,CLabour Government accused of
OL,4,C'betraying' Troubles victims
OL,6,F"The decision marks the continued
OL,7,Fdilution of the categorical pledge by
OL,8,FLabour prior to the election that they
OL,9,Fwould right the wrong of the last
OL,10,FGovernment on legacy."
OL,12,FMs Teggart said the ICRIR "does not
OL,13,Fhave the confidence of the community
OL,14,Fit is supposed to serve".
OL,16,F"The policy of this UK Government now
OL,17,Fappears to be partial repeal so they
OL,18,Fcan prop up a body established by the
OL,19,Flast government and maintained by this
OL,20,FGovernment," she said.
