OL,3,CLabour Government accused of
OL,4,C'betraying' Troubles victims
OL,6,F"The Secretary of State should have
OL,7,Fscrapped the Act in full. Dragging out
OL,8,Fthis process is only causing
OL,9,Funnecessary delays to victims awaiting
OL,10,Fthe truth and justice they are
OL,11,Fentitled to.
OL,13,F"Dealing with the past in a human
OL,14,Frights compliant way will be a litmus
OL,15,Ftest for this Government. It will tell
OL,16,FTroubles victims, society here and the
OL,17,Finternational human rights community
OL,18,Fhow serious this Government is about
OL,19,Frespecting and protecting rights.
