OL,6,F"Our message is clear, repeal should
OL,7,Fmean repeal. We want to see two pieces
OL,8,Fof legislation, one to repeal the Act
OL,9,Fand the other to replace it."
OL,11,FShe added: "It is essential that the
OL,12,FIrish Government continues to stand
OL,13,Fwith victims through that Interstate
OL,14,Fcase."
OL,16,FDarragh Mackin of Phoenix Law said the
OL,17,FGovernment "lost in the High Court,
OL,18,Flost in the Court of Appeal", and said
OL,19,Fthey have faith the Government "will
OL,20,Fagain lose in the Supreme Court".
